2026-03-04 16:02:17:0486 [GENERATION] {{"run_id": "1772640110312-38b34276", "task": "numero_primo", "attempt": 1, "tokens_input": 149, "tokens_output": 85, "tokens_total": 234}} <code>
    def is_prime(n):
        if n < 2:
            return False
        if n == 2:
            return True
        if n % 2 == 0:
            return False
        for i in range(3, int(n**0.5) + 1, 2):
            if n % i == 0:
                return False
        return True
    </code>

